{"tid":1466010,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"機場藍衫其中一個身份係記者，唔代表唔係共產黨員","createTime":"2019-08-13T16:28:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T16:39:20.000Z","uid":204246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"711e165323d7b8ff4a9de70f3242eb30fa3eca66","tid":1466010,"uid":204246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:28:40.000Z","msg":"大陸所有既大公司/企業都會因應中央要求<br />\n設立共產黨專屬部門，一來用黎監控該公司企業<br />\n二來有國家任務既時候可以由中央直接指揮<br />\n所以好多大陸大公司大企業既員工有多重身份<br />\n發生左既事就唔好再指責對錯<br />\n下次唔好再犯就可以，冷靜制服佢之後<br />\n盡可能係佢身上套資料遠遠比傷害佢身體好"},{"pid":"122dd4102b690813e153a8c20a84c514540e6617","tid":1466010,"uid":204246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:30:20.000Z","msg":"不分化不指責"},{"pid":"d87819f150cc9e1f2261665985e188817aa94144","tid":1466010,"uid":204246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:31:28.000Z","msg":"不分化不指責"},{"pid":"ff72a6415e16bcbefa43c739e6fd3e76f4811598","tid":1466010,"uid":204246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:33:26.000Z","msg":"不分化不指責"},{"pid":"b27ccba4c926610ca9285b0ca71215c39cd4cc24","tid":1466010,"uid":204246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:34:10.000Z","msg":"不分化不指責"},{"pid":"b364e8aa1fa5bd8a06e1df1488eb727ceeee0c8e","tid":1466010,"uid":204246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:34:23.000Z","msg":"不分化不指責"},{"pid":"3063713474a7303807f404c960b463f4734d6af7","tid":1466010,"uid":204246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:34:41.000Z","msg":"不分化不指責"},{"pid":"d59c7d1e78f0271b599164f2b6126c40288a1d76","tid":1466010,"uid":204246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:34:53.000Z","msg":"不分化不指責"},{"pid":"12d4127993c769d81afdd84c368053f6f627ee8d","tid":1466010,"uid":204246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:35:10.000Z","msg":"不分化不指責"},{"pid":"c241b36e228450af15ec17b1aad3e4e72912d